284
00:12:16.720 --> 00:12:17.640
You see that in verse eight.

285
00:12:17.640 --> 00:12:19.440
He's saying lead me in your righteousness

286
00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:23.680
because of my enemies.

287
00:12:23.680 --> 00:12:27.680
All right, so he's praying that the Lord in contrast

288
00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:29.480
