290
00:12:33.440 --> 00:12:35.560
So another reason we should ask the Lord

291
00:12:35.560 --> 00:12:40.560
to lead us in righteousness is because he is holy

292
00:12:41.000 --> 00:12:43.640
and because sin is deadly.

293
00:12:43.640 --> 00:12:44.760
Let's put it simply.

294
00:12:44.760 --> 00:12:46.840
God is holy, sin is deadly.

295
00:12:46.840 --> 00:12:47.680
We see that here.

296
00:12:47.680 --> 00:12:52.080
You see the holiness of God here in verse four for example.

297
00:12:53.280 --> 00:12:56.560
He says for you are not a God who delights in wickedness.

298
00:12:56.600 --> 00:13:00.120
Evil may not dwell with you.

299
00:13:01.000 --> 00:13:03.000
Or you see in verse seven.

300
00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:04.200
He says, but I through the abundance

301
00:13:04.200 --> 00:13:06.160
of your steadfast love will enter your house.

302
00:13:06.160 --> 00:13:09.840
I will bow down toward your holy temple

303
00:13:09.840 --> 00:13:11.280
in the fear of you.

304
00:13:11.280 --> 00:13:12.960
So when he's approaching God,

305
00:13:12.960 --> 00:13:16.200
he remembers that God's dwelling place is holy.

306
00:13:16.200 --> 00:13:19.140
