00:20:17.580 --> 00:20:19.540
Notice what he says in verse 10.

453
00:20:19.540 --> 00:20:21.500
He says, make them bear their guilt of God.

454
00:20:21.500 --> 00:20:25.200
Let them fall by their own counsels.

455
00:20:26.060 --> 00:20:29.700
So here's the judgment that God is giving here.

456
00:20:29.700 --> 00:20:31.420
This is what he's praying for here.

457
00:20:31.420 --> 00:20:35.960
It's a judgment to let them chase after what they want.

458
00:20:35.960 --> 00:20:40.180
Let them follow the path they are already going down.

459
00:20:40.180 --> 00:20:42.580
So it's God's judgment, in other words,

460
00:20:42.580 --> 00:20:46.380
