466
00:21:02.500 --> 00:21:05.500
So scripture speaks of God's judgment in that way,

467
00:21:05.500 --> 00:21:08.180
giving people what they want rather than

468
00:21:08.180 --> 00:21:09.620
the path of righteousness,

469
00:21:09.620 --> 00:21:12.340
the good that he is leading his people in.

470
00:21:12.340 --> 00:21:14.620
But how does this apply to us?

471
00:21:15.620 --> 00:21:18.820
Well, here's what the psalmist is not calling us to do.

