788
00:35:29.720 --> 00:35:32.000
knowing that we could have never approached you

789
00:35:32.000 --> 00:35:35.160
on our own, in our own sinful condition.

790
00:35:36.160 --> 00:35:38.400
But Lord we thank you so much for the hope

791
00:35:38.640 --> 00:35:43.320
and the refuge that we have in Jesus.

792
00:35:43.320 --> 00:35:46.480
Lord we thank you that Lord

793
00:35:46.480 --> 00:35:49.280
that you've shown us your love in Him

794
00:35:49.280 --> 00:35:51.080
and that you bring us to Him and show us

795
00:35:51.080 --> 00:35:53.320
we can have a refuge in Him

796
00:35:53.320 --> 00:35:55.840
and we can know a life in your loving home

797
00:35:55.840 --> 00:35:57.800
and instead of running away from your holiness

798
00:35:57.800 --> 00:36:02.160
Lord we can run to you and know more of the joy

799
00:36:02.160 --> 00:36:05.680
that is given to us in you.

800
00:36:06.680 --> 00:36:10.120
So Lord we thank you that when we come to your throne

801
00:36:11.240 --> 00:36:13.000
the throne of you, our holy God

802
00:36:13.000 --> 00:36:16.160
we can find it to be a throne of grace

803
00:36:16.160 --> 00:36:19.720
where we find help in our time of need.

804
00:36:19.720 --> 00:36:24.480
So Lord I pray that you'd help us to be a people

805
00:36:24.480 --> 00:36:27.320
who know what it is to be saved

806
00:36:27.320 --> 00:36:28.840
and to rejoice in the salvation

807
00:36:28.840 --> 00:36:31.080
provided for us in Jesus.

808
00:36:31.080 --> 00:36:33.360
And Lord I pray that we would be a people

809
00:36:33.400 --> 00:36:37.280
who follow you praying Lord lead us in your righteousness

810
00:36:37.280 --> 00:36:41.000
and as we do that we would rejoice more and more in you.

811
00:36:41.000 --> 00:36:43.000
Pray this in Jesus name, amen.

